text: Party logo, 2017-2018 Independence Party of the Czech Republic (, SNČR) previously called Referendum on the European Union () is a Czech Eurosceptic political party founded and led by František Matějka, former member of the Party of Free Citizens. František Matějka resigned to leader's position on May 22, 2020. ==Election results== ===European Parliament=== {| class="wikitable" style="text-align: center" ! Year ! # of total votes ! Vote % !
